601
01:00:38,260 --> 01:00:38,760
 je li,

602
01:00:38,760 --> 01:00:39,800
 opet istaknuti,

603
01:00:39,800 --> 01:00:40,800
 da središnja,

604
01:00:40,800 --> 01:00:42,740
 ili temeljna poruka

605
01:00:42,740 --> 01:00:44,480
 knjige otkrivenja,

606
01:00:44,940 --> 01:00:47,780
 a to je da zlo

607
01:00:47,780 --> 01:00:51,220
 nije trajno,

608
01:00:51,220 --> 01:00:51,540
 dakle,

609
01:00:51,540 --> 01:00:53,520
 nema trajnu vrijednost,

610
01:00:53,520 --> 01:00:53,840
 dakle,

611
01:00:53,840 --> 01:00:55,980
 zlo je uvijek parcijalno,

612
01:00:55,980 --> 01:00:56,320
 dakle,

613
01:00:56,320 --> 01:00:58,360
 ono je agresivno,

614
01:00:58,360 --> 01:00:59,680
 ono kad čovjeka pogodi,

615
01:00:59,680 --> 01:01:02,320
 čovjeka naravno osjeća,

616
01:01:02,320 --> 01:01:05,060
 ali zlo nikada ne zahvaća

617
01:01:05,060 --> 01:01:06,560
 u potpunosti

618
