638
01:01:44,020 --> 01:01:44,880
 ili snagu

639
01:01:44,880 --> 01:01:47,120
 da ostane

640
01:01:47,120 --> 01:01:48,260
 vječno,

641
01:01:48,260 --> 01:01:48,980
 ili to je

642
01:01:48,980 --> 01:01:50,960
 to je temeljna poruka

643
01:01:50,960 --> 01:01:52,760
 knjige

644
01:01:52,760 --> 01:01:54,200
 otkrivenja.

645
01:01:54,200 --> 01:01:55,520
 Tako da

646
01:01:55,520 --> 01:01:57,440
 nekako je

647
01:01:57,440 --> 01:02:01,020
 pogrešno

648
01:02:01,020 --> 01:02:02,140
 kada,

649
01:02:02,140 --> 01:02:03,180
 recimo,

650
01:02:03,180 --> 01:02:04,880
 priljev apokaliptični,

651
01:02:04,880 --> 01:02:06,640
 tako nešto upotrebljavamo

652
01:02:06,640 --> 01:02:09,060
 za katastrofe,

653
01:02:09,060 --> 01:02:10,400
 ako mislimo da se radi

654
01:02:10,400 --> 01:02:12,140
 o nekakvim potpunim,

655
01:02:12,140 --> 01:02:14,820
 bezizlaznim katastrofama,

656
01:02:14,820 --> 01:02:16,660
 ali to se čuje ovako u govoru,

657
01:02:16,660 --> 01:02:17,380
 naravno,

658
01:02:17,380 --> 01:02:19,960
 za takav način izražavanja

659
01:02:19,960 --> 01:02:21,180
 u knjizi

660
01:02:21,180 --> 01:02:21,500
 otkrivenja,

661
01:02:21,500 --> 01:02:22,300
 otkrivenja,

662
01:02:22,300 --> 01:02:23,260
 ili postoji

663
01:02:23,260 --> 01:02:24,400
 argument,

664
01:02:24,400 --> 01:02:25,560
 jer knjiga otkrivenja

665
01:02:25,560 --> 01:02:25,980
 doista

666
01:02:25,980 --> 01:02:28,080
 o tome govori,

667
01:02:28,080 --> 01:02:29,040
 ali naravno,

