01:02:40,040 --> 01:02:42,440
 neka tendencija

678
01:02:42,440 --> 01:02:43,760
 da se

679
01:02:43,760 --> 01:02:45,120
 ono što piše

680
01:02:45,120 --> 01:02:45,540
 u knjizi

681
01:02:45,540 --> 01:02:46,440
 otkrivenja

682
01:02:46,440 --> 01:02:47,600
 poveže

683
01:02:47,600 --> 01:02:48,340
 sa nekim

684
01:02:48,340 --> 01:02:49,880
 točno određenim

685
01:02:49,880 --> 01:02:50,900
 događajima

686
01:02:50,900 --> 01:02:52,160
 ili osobama

687
01:02:52,160 --> 01:02:54,260
 i tako dalje,

688
01:02:54,260 --> 01:02:56,500
 knjiga otkrivenja

689
01:02:56,500 --> 01:02:57,740
 to ne radi.

690
01:02:57,740 --> 01:02:58,660
 Dakle,

691
01:02:58,660 --> 01:02:59,900
 knjiga otkrivenja

692
